head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h1>Body-Tell 对齐 VoxTell v1.1 实施计划</h1>\n    <p class=\"meta\">日期：2026-05-24；目标：让 Body-Tell 在结构和权重语义上尽量对齐 VoxTell v1.1，优先支持 VoxTell checkpoint 复用，而不是只做到 tensor shape 能加载。</p>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <section>\n      <h2>核验结论</h2>\n      <div class=\"callout\">\n        <p><strong>原差异报告中的核心不一致真实存在。</strong> 其中最影响 VoxTell 权重复用的是两类问题：一类是参数量和模块拓扑明显不同，例如 encoder/decoder；另一类是参数 shape 一致但 forward 语义不同，例如 transformer decoder。</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"cards\">\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>Body-Tell 当前参数</span><strong>328.98M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>VoxTell v1.1 参数</span><strong>440.03M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>Body encoder</span><strong>8.49M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>VoxTell encoder</span><strong>90.30M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>Transformer 参数</span><strong>251.86M</strong></div>\n        <div class=\"card\"><span>最高风险</span><strong>shape 同而语义不同</strong></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr><th>差异点</th><th>核验结果</th><th>对权重复用的影响</th><th>证据位置</th></tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Transformer decoder</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 使用 <code>activation=\"gelu\"</code>，pre-norm path 执行 self-attention；VoxTell 默认 <code>relu</code>，active <code>forward_pre</code> 跳过 self-attention，只做 cross-attention 和 FFN。</td>\n            <td>参数名和 shape 可 100% 对上，但加载 VoxTell 权重后语义不等价。小模型同权重实验输出最大绝对差为 <code>0.9258</code>。</td>\n            <td><code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:69</code>、<code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:137</code>、<code>VoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:224</code></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Encoder backbone</td>\n            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 是 5-stage 手写 ConvBlock；VoxTell 是 6-stage <code>ResidualEncoder</code>，features 为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320,320]</code>，blocks 为 <code>[1,3,4,6,6,6]</code>。</td>\n            <td>当前 encoder 无法复用 VoxTell encoder 权重，也很可能限制性能上限。这个差异不是“轻量配置”，而是 backbone 类型不同。</td>\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
