{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_15","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc 'grep -nE \"Projection Shape Baseline|Body-Tell current|VoxTell source default|VoxTell v1.1 checkpoint-derived|P6 Whitelist Input|Required exact skips|Conditional skips|Machine-Readable\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/audit_voxtell_alignment.html'","aggregated_output":"31:    <h2>Projection Shape Baseline</h2>\n32:    <p><strong>Body-Tell current</strong>: <code>num_heads=32</code>, actual fused projection stages <code>4</code> from configured <code>5</code>; prefix is <code>mask_projections</code>, target aligned prefix is <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code>.</p>\n37:    <p><strong>VoxTell source default</strong>: <code>num_heads=1</code>. This is the class default in <code>voxtell_model.py</code>, not necessarily the shipped v1.1 checkpoint profile.</p>\n43:    <p><strong>VoxTell v1.1 checkpoint-derived</strong>: predictor override <code>num_heads=32</code>; checkpoint inferred <code>num_heads=32</code>; pos_embed shape <code>(1728, 1, 2048)</code>.</p>\n68:    <h2>P6 Whitelist Input</h2>\n69:    <h3>Required exact skips</h3>\n70:    <table><thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>pos_embed</code></td><td>Body-Tell current non-192^3 crop uses dynamic positional encoding.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n71:    <h3>Conditional skips</h3>\n73:    <ul><li>checkpoint-derived num_heads matches Body-Tell current num_heads; do not skip project_to_decoder_channels.* or decoder mask-fusion keys for this reason</li></ul>\n77:    <h2>Machine-Readable Audit Payload</h2>\n5973:      &quot;checkpoint-derived num_heads matches Body-Tell current num_heads; do not skip project_to_decoder_channels.* or decoder mask-fusion keys for this reason&quot;\n5979:        &quot;reason&quot;: &quot;Body-Tell current non-192^3 crop uses dynamic positional encoding.&quot;\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_12","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"grep -nE \\\"SP-A\\\\.P0|SP-A P0|P0|golden|whitelist|num_heads|projection\\\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html\"","aggregated_output":"Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:224:            <td>Mask projections（含 <code>num_heads</code>）</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:225:            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> 两层根因：(1) Body-Tell 配置写 5，但运行时被 <code>min(num_maskformer_stages, len(encoder_channels)-1)</code> 截成 4 级；(2) Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）vs VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell_model.py:74</code>）。两者乘积决定实际 projection 输出。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:226:            <td>Body-Tell 实际输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>（<code>channels × 32</code>，stage 0 例外）；VoxTell 实际输出 <strong><code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级</strong>（<code>channels × 1</code>）。<strong>原报告写 VoxTell 最高级 <code>10240</code> 是错误的。</strong> 即使 encoder 升到 6 级、stage 截断消除，<code>num_heads</code> 不同会导致 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与下游 mask fusion 模块的 shape 不匹配，权重无法直接复用。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:280:            <td><code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> + <code>num_heads</code></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:281:            <td>使用 VoxTell 命名，替代当前 <code>mask_projections</code>；5 级；输出维度 = encoder 各级 channels × <code>num_heads</code>。<strong>条件性对齐</strong>（父表 #13，域差异豁免）：如果实验目标是<strong>直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 和 mask fusion 权重</strong>，则必须设 <code>num_heads=1</code>，实际输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级；如果仅做结构对齐而不复用这部分权重（更符合 Body-Tell occupancy grid 任务的需求，因为 <code>num_heads=32</code> 提供 32× mask fusion 容量是为该任务调过的），则保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:282:            <td>选 <code>num_heads=1</code>：直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code>。选保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>：必须把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 全部加入跳过白名单，并在 audit 中登记\"为保留 Body-Tell mask fusion 容量而跳过这部分权重复用\"。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:296:      <h3>P0：建立兼容性基线</h3>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:298:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 新增）<code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 显式审计</strong>：新增 <code>Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code>（如果与已有 <code>scripts/parameter_audit.py</code> 重合，应共享 utilities）。<strong>脚本第一步必须打印两侧 <code>num_heads</code> 值和每级 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code> 实际输出 shape</strong>，确认 VoxTell 为 <code>num_heads=1</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code> 量级，Body-Tell 当前为 <code>num_heads=32</code> + 输出 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192]</code>。该审计是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（路径 A vs 路径 B）的输入材料，audit 完成后才能在 P4 选定路径。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:300:        <li>新增 transformer golden test <code>Body-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py</code>：同一小尺寸 state dict、相同输入、dropout=0 时，Body-Tell aligned transformer 输出必须与 VoxTell transformer 完全一致或在 <code>1e-6</code> 内。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:303:      <p>验收：当前轻量模型仍可跑旧测试；新增审计能明确报告哪些 key 会加载、哪些 key 因 policy 跳过；<strong>且 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（设为 1 / 保留 32）必须先于 P4 落地</strong>。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:331:      <h3>P4：对齐 projection、mask head、<code>num_heads</code> 决议和 forward 排列</h3>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:332:      <div class=\"callout warnbox\"><strong>P4 <code>num_heads</code> 决议（父表 #13，域差异豁免）</strong>：在执行 P4 前必须先选定路径——\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:334:          <li><strong>路径 A（强对齐，复用权重）</strong>：<code>num_heads=1</code>，projection 输出 <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>，可直接加载 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重。代价：失去 Body-Tell 现有 32× mask fusion 容量。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:335:          <li><strong>路径 B（结构对齐但放弃这部分权重复用，推荐）</strong>：保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，projection 输出维持 <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>（encoder 升 6 级后扩展），<code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重 <strong>不加载</strong>，加入 P6 跳过白名单。理由：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid 与 VoxTell 医学影像任务差异显著，这部分权重的可迁移性弱，而 mask fusion 容量对当前任务更有价值。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:337:        默认建议路径 B，并在 P0 audit 中显式打印决议来源。如果 audit 没有给出明确收益对比，<strong>保持现状（路径 B）即可，不强制对齐 <code>num_heads</code></strong>。\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:340:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）<code>num_heads</code> 决议生效</strong>：按上方选定路径执行。路径 A 需把配置 <code>num_heads</code> 默认值改为 <code>1</code>，同时审计 Body-Tell 中所有依赖 <code>num_heads</code> 的 reshape（如 <code>view(B, num_heads, C//num_heads)</code>）和 decoder stage 内 <code>input_features + num_heads</code> 的通道拼接是否正确退化；路径 B 不改 <code>num_heads</code>，但需要在 P6 把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入跳过白名单。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:341:        <li>把当前 <code>project_visual_embed</code> 改为 VoxTell 命名 <code>project_bottleneck_embed</code>；把 <code>mask_projections</code> 改为 <code>project_to_decoder_channels</code>。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:342:        <li>encoder 变为 6-stage 后，projection stage 自然恢复为 5 级，不再用 <code>len(encoder_channels)-1</code> 隐式截断配置。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:346:      <p>验收：5 个 projection 输出维度按选定路径（路径 A: <code>[32, 64, 128, 256, 320]</code>；路径 B: <code>[32, 2048, 4096, 8192, 10240]</code>）；非立方输入的输出 shape 与 target mask 完全一致；mask fusion 模块在选定 <code>num_heads</code> 下有显式单测；audit 报告记录选定路径与原因。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:374:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 修订）显式 <code>unexpected_keys</code> 白名单</strong>：调用 <code>model.load_state_dict(state_dict, strict=False)</code> 后，断言 <code>set(unexpected_keys) ⊆ POLICY_ALLOWED_SKIP</code>（默认 <code>{\"pos_embed\"}</code>；若 P4 决定保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，再扩展到 <code>{\"pos_embed\", \"project_to_decoder_channels.*\", \"decoder.<mask_fusion_keys>\"}</code>）。<strong>任何 shape mismatch 必须抛错，不得静默跳过</strong>；<code>missing_keys</code> 不为空时打印完整列表并要求显式确认。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:400:            <td>只加载 transformer / text / projection 权重</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:406:            <td>加载 encoder、decoder、projection、transformer；按 policy 跳过或加载 <code>pos_embed</code></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:480:        <li><strong>（2026-05-24 上调）P0 <code>num_heads</code> 与 projection shape 审计</strong>。这是父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 决议的输入材料；不在 P4 落地前完成审计，P3/P4/P6 都会建立在未经确认的输出维度假设上。允许 audit 结论是\"保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>\"（路径 B），但必须显式记录。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:181:    <p class=\"note warn\">2026-05-24 修订：原 11 项基础上新增 #12 BCE+Dice loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code> mismatch（Body-Tell=32 vs VoxTell=1）。其中 #13 同时修正了原 SP-A 中\"VoxTell projection 输出 <code>[32,2048,4096,8192,10240]</code>\"的错误表述（实际为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320]</code> 量级，<code>num_heads</code> 才是根因）。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:182:    <div class=\"note warn\"><strong>域差异豁免（2026-05-24 重要约束）</strong>：Body-Tell 处理 occupancy grid，VoxTell 处理医学影像（CT/MRI/PET）。任务输入模态、特征统计、噪声特性都不同。<strong>本计划中\"对齐\"是手段不是目的，目的是支持 VoxTell 权重复用与实现一致性。任何一项不一致，若实现阶段 audit 后发现对齐会损害性能、或对当前任务没有可观察收益、或与权重复用无关，允许显式跳过并在子计划中记录原因。</strong> #12（loss 公式）与 #13（<code>num_heads</code>）尤其适用此豁免。</div>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:206:          <td>模型结构对齐：transformer decoder 语义、ResidualEncoder、VoxTellDecoder、5-scale projection、位置编码策略、VoxTell 权重加载入口、训练实验矩阵。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:227:    <p>按下面顺序开工。SP-C 不需要整体等到 SP-A/SP-B 完成；只有 deep supervision、长训通过和最终评估需要等结构与 patch-level sampler 到位。<strong>（2026-05-24 修订）阶段 1 新增 SP-A P0 audit 作为首项；阶段 2 P4 内部包含 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议（路径 A vs 路径 B），决议依赖 P0 audit 输出；阶段 3 Task 5 与 P6 的具体实现内容随 P4 决议变化。</strong></p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:242:              <li><strong><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P0</a>（新增首项）</strong>：建立兼容性基线 audit—— <code>num_heads</code> + projection shape 双侧打印、transformer golden test、weight key audit。产出三份输入材料：(a) 父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议输入，(b) P1 transformer parity 验收测试，(c) P6 权重加载白名单。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:243:              <li><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P1</a>：Transformer decoder 语义对齐（验收使用 P0 的 transformer golden test）。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:248:          <td>可以并行。P0 audit 不修改 Body-Tell 代码，只输出审计材料；P1 transformer 改动可与 P0 同步进行。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:249:          <td>形成可复现训练 loop 骨架；<strong>完成 P0 后必须显式记录 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议（默认路径 B：保留 32）</strong>；但还不能宣称 paper-aligned 长训通过。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:255:              <li>SP-A P2-P5：Residual encoder、VoxTellDecoder、projection/forward 排列、位置编码策略（<code>dynamic_hwd</code> 默认，适配 <code>[129,108,256]</code>）。<strong>P4 内部按 P0 选定的 <code>num_heads</code> 路径执行</strong>——路径 A 改 <code>num_heads=1</code>；路径 B 保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入 P6 跳过白名单候选。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:279:              <li>SP-A P7：random / prompt-only / full 三组 warm-start 对照实验。若 P4 选路径 B，<code>full</code> 实际等价于\"除 mask fusion 与 projection 外全部加载\"，需在实验日志显式区分。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:288:    <p class=\"note warn\">关键路径串行依赖（2026-05-24 修订后）：<strong>SP-A P0 audit → P4 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议 → P6 跳过白名单</strong>；<strong>SP-A P3 → SP-C Task 5</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3/4 → Step 5 → Step 6</strong>。其余环节可并行。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:293:    <p>下表是本文件的核心。每一项不一致都必须被某一个子计划领走；当前 13 项已全部分发，其中结构类由 SP-A 负责（含 #13 <code>num_heads</code>，标记为条件性对齐），数据构造类由 SP-B 负责，训练机制与评估协议类由 SP-C 负责（含 #12 loss 等价性，标记为 audit 后可跳过）。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:350:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P3/P4 — VoxTellDecoder + projection</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:378:          <td><span class=\"tag warn\"><code>num_heads</code> mismatch<br><span class=\"small\">（条件性对齐）</span></span></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:379:          <td>VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>）；Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）。projection 输出 = <code>channels × num_heads</code>，因此原 SP-A \"VoxTell 输出 <code>10240</code>\"的说法错误，实际为 <code>320</code> 量级。<strong>域差异豁免</strong>：<code>num_heads=32</code> 给 Body-Tell mask fusion 提供 32× 容量，是为 occupancy grid 任务设计的；强行降到 1 可能损害 capacity。<strong>对齐前提</strong>：只有在\"目标是直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重\"的实验中才必要；若仅做结构对齐（不复用这部分权重），可以保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，但<strong>必须在 SP-A P0 audit 中显式打印 num_heads 并把这些 key 加入跳过白名单</strong>，避免错误判断为权重已加载。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:380:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P0 + P4 — num_heads 审计与对齐决议</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:403:    <p class=\"note\">关键串行依赖（2026-05-24 修订后）：<strong>SP-A P0 audit → P4 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议 → P6 跳过白名单组装</strong>；<strong>SP-A P0 transformer golden test → P1 验收</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3 / Step 4</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 4 → Step 5 → Step 6</strong>；<strong>SP-A P3 → SP-C Task 5 deep supervision</strong>；<strong>SP-A P2/P3/P4 → SP-A P6</strong>。SP-A 结构对齐与 SP-B 数据构造可并行，但二者必须早于 deep supervision、权重加载和正式长训。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:417:        <li><strong>结构闸门</strong>（SP-A P0 完成后）：<code>audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code> 报告 transformer parity test 通过（输出差异 &lt; <code>1e-6</code>，dropout=0）；<code>num_heads</code> 与每级 projection 实际 shape 已显式打印。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:427:    <p><strong>可以按本文件开始执行。</strong> 13 项明确不一致已全部分发：SP-A 覆盖结构类（含 #13 <code>num_heads</code>），SP-B 覆盖数据构造类，SP-C 覆盖训练机制、checkpoint、评估协议和测试矩阵（含 #12 loss 等价性 audit）。<strong>#12 和 #13 适用域差异豁免</strong>：audit 后允许在保留 Body-Tell 当前实现并显式记录偏差的前提下跳过对齐。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:428:    <p>短期优先顺序是：SP-A P0（含 <code>num_heads</code> + projection 实际 shape 审计）、SP-B Step 1、SP-C Task 0-4 并行启动；随后推进 SP-A P1-P5 和 SP-B Step 2-Step 4；最后启用 SP-C Task 5（含 BCE+Dice 等价性 audit，可仅记录偏差）、权重加载、评估与训练实验。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:429:    <p class=\"small\">本报告仅维护审计与索引，未修改训练代码。2026-05-24 修订：增列 #12 loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code>（带域差异豁免），新增 baseline 评估闸门。</p>\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_13","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '261,620p' Body-Tell/scripts/audit_voxtell_alignment.py\"","aggregated_output":"        else:\n            mismatched.append(\n                {\n                    \"name\": name,\n                    \"body_shape\": body_shape,\n                    \"checkpoint_shape\": checkpoint_shape,\n                }\n            )\n\n    missing_in_checkpoint = sorted(set(body_shapes) - set(checkpoint_shapes))\n    unexpected_in_checkpoint = sorted(set(checkpoint_shapes) - set(body_shapes))\n    prefix_rows = []\n    for prefix in sorted({_prefix(name) for name in set(body_shapes) | set(checkpoint_shapes)}):\n        body_keys = {name for name in body_shapes if _prefix(name) == prefix}\n        checkpoint_keys = {name for name in checkpoint_shapes if _prefix(name) == prefix}\n        matching_keys = {name for name in matching if _prefix(name) == prefix}\n        prefix_rows.append(\n            {\n                \"prefix\": prefix,\n                \"body_keys\": len(body_keys),\n                \"checkpoint_keys\": len(checkpoint_keys),\n                \"shape_compatible_same_name\": len(matching_keys),\n            }\n        )\n\n    matched_param_count = sum(_numel(body_shapes[name]) for name in matching)\n    body_param_count = sum(_numel(shape) for shape in body_shapes.values())\n\n    return {\n        \"available\": True,\n        \"matching_count\": len(matching),\n        \"mismatch_count\": len(mismatched),\n        \"missing_in_checkpoint_count\": len(missing_in_checkpoint),\n        \"unexpected_in_checkpoint_count\": len(unexpected_in_checkpoint),\n        \"matching\": matching,\n        \"mismatched\": mismatched,\n        \"missing_in_checkpoint\": missing_in_checkpoint,\n        \"unexpected_in_checkpoint\": unexpected_in_checkpoint,\n        \"prefix_rows\": prefix_rows,\n        \"matched_param_count\": matched_param_count,\n        \"body_param_count\": body_param_count,\n    }\n\n\ndef build_whitelist_input(\n    *,\n    pos_embed_policy: str,\n    body_num_heads: int,\n    source_default_num_heads: int,\n    checkpoint_num_heads: int | None,\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    effective_checkpoint_heads = checkpoint_num_heads\n    exact_skips = []\n    conditional_skips = []\n    no_skip_notes = []\n\n    if pos_embed_policy == \"dynamic_hwd\":\n        exact_skips.append(\n            {\n                \"pattern\": \"pos_embed\",\n                \"reason\": \"Body-Tell current non-192^3 crop uses dynamic positional encoding.\",\n            }\n        )\n\n    if effective_checkpoint_heads is not None and effective_checkpoint_heads != body_num_heads:\n        conditional_skips.extend(\n            [\n                {\n                    \"pattern\": \"project_to_decoder_channels.[1-4].*\",\n                    \"reason\": \"projection output channels scale with num_heads for stages 1-4\",\n                },\n                {\n                    \"pattern\": \"decoder.transpconvs.[1-4].*\",\n                    \"reason\": \"intermediate decoder inputs include num_heads fused mask channels\",\n                },\n                {\n                    \"pattern\": \"decoder.seg_layers.*\",\n                    \"reason\": \"segmentation heads take input_features_skip + num_heads channels\",\n                },\n            ]\n        )\n    elif effective_checkpoint_heads is not None:\n        no_skip_notes.append(\n            \"checkpoint-derived num_heads matches Body-Tell current num_heads; \"\n            \"do not skip project_to_decoder_channels.* or decoder mask-fusion keys for this reason\"\n        )\n\n    if source_default_num_heads != body_num_heads:\n        conditional_skips.append(\n            {\n                \"pattern\": \"project_to_decoder_channels.[1-4].*, decoder.transpconvs.[1-4].*, decoder.seg_layers.*\",\n                \"reason\": (\n                    \"only apply if loading a checkpoint generated from the VoxTellModel source \"\n                    \"default num_heads=1 into a Body-Tell num_heads=32 model\"\n                ),\n            }\n        )\n\n    return {\n        \"pos_embed_policy\": pos_embed_policy,\n        \"body_num_heads\": body_num_heads,\n        \"voxtell_source_default_num_heads\": source_default_num_heads,\n        \"voxtell_checkpoint_num_heads\": checkpoint_num_heads,\n        \"required_exact_skip_patterns\": exact_skips,\n        \"conditional_skip_patterns\": conditional_skips,\n        \"no_skip_notes\": no_skip_notes,\n    }\n\n\ndef make_audit(args: argparse.Namespace) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    body_config = load_body_config(args.config)\n    body_rows = body_projection_rows(body_config)\n    source_info = parse_voxtell_model_source(VOXTELL_ROOT / \"voxtell\" / \"model\" / \"voxtell_model.py\")\n    predictor_overrides = parse_voxtell_predictor_overrides(\n        VOXTELL_ROOT / \"voxtell\" / \"inference\" / \"predictor.py\"\n    )\n\n    defaults = source_info[\"defaults\"]\n    decoder_configs = source_info[\"decoder_configs\"]\n    source_default_num_heads = int(defaults[\"num_heads\"])\n    source_default_hidden_dim = int(defaults[\"project_to_decoder_hidden_dim\"])\n    source_default_num_stages = int(defaults[\"num_maskformer_stages\"])\n    source_rows = voxtell_projection_rows(\n        decoder_configs,\n        source_default_num_stages,\n        source_default_num_heads,\n        source_default_hidden_dim,\n    )\n\n    predictor_num_heads = int(predictor_overrides.get(\"num_heads\", source_default_num_heads))\n    predictor_hidden_dim = int(\n        predictor_overrides.get(\"project_to_decoder_hidden_dim\", source_default_hidden_dim)\n    )\n    predictor_num_stages = int(\n        predictor_overrides.get(\"num_maskformer_stages\", source_default_num_stages)\n    )\n    predictor_rows = voxtell_projection_rows(\n        decoder_configs,\n        predictor_num_stages,\n        predictor_num_heads,\n        predictor_hidden_dim,\n    )\n\n    checkpoint = None if args.skip_checkpoint else load_checkpoint_shapes(args.voxtell_dir)\n    checkpoint_num_heads = None\n    if checkpoint and checkpoint[\"available\"]:\n        checkpoint_num_heads = infer_num_heads_from_projection_rows(\n            checkpoint[\"projection_rows\"],\n            decoder_configs,\n        )\n        for row in checkpoint[\"projection_rows\"]:\n            stage = row[\"stage\"]\n            row[\"channels\"] = int(decoder_configs[stage][\"channels\"])\n\n    body_shapes = None if args.skip_state_dict_compare else load_body_state_shapes(body_config)\n    checkpoint_shapes = (\n        checkpoint.get(\"state_shapes\")\n        if checkpoint is not None and checkpoint.get(\"available\")\n        else None\n    )\n    state_compare = compare_state_shapes(checkpoint_shapes, body_shapes)\n\n    whitelist_input = build_whitelist_input(\n        pos_embed_policy=args.pos_embed_policy,\n        body_num_heads=int(body_config.num_heads),\n        source_default_num_heads=source_default_num_heads,\n        checkpoint_num_heads=checkpoint_num_heads,\n    )\n\n    return {\n        \"body\": {\n            \"config_path\": str(args.config),\n            \"num_heads\": int(body_config.num_heads),\n            \"num_maskformer_stages_config\": int(body_config.num_maskformer_stages),\n            \"fused_stage_count_actual\": len(body_rows),\n            \"encoder_channels\": list(body_config.encoder_channels),\n            \"projection_prefix\": \"mask_projections\",\n            \"target_projection_prefix\": \"project_to_decoder_channels\",\n            \"projection_rows\": body_rows,\n        },\n        \"voxtell\": {\n            \"source_default\": {\n                \"num_heads\": source_default_num_heads,\n                \"hidden_dim\": source_default_hidden_dim,\n                \"projection_rows\": source_rows,\n            },\n            \"predictor_v1_1\": {\n                \"num_heads\": predictor_num_heads,\n                \"hidden_dim\": predictor_hidden_dim,\n                \"projection_rows\": predictor_rows,\n                \"overrides\": predictor_overrides,\n            },\n            \"checkpoint\": checkpoint,\n            \"checkpoint_num_heads\": checkpoint_num_heads,\n        },\n        \"state_compare_current_body_vs_checkpoint\": state_compare,\n        \"whitelist_input\": whitelist_input,\n    }\n\n\ndef fmt_shape(shape: Any) -> str:\n    if shape is None:\n        return \"n/a\"\n    return \"(\" + \", \".join(str(int(x)) for x in shape) + \")\"\n\n\ndef projection_line(row: dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n    return (\n        f\"  stage {row['stage']}: channels={row.get('channels', 'n/a')} \"\n        f\"output_dim={row['output_dim']} weight={fmt_shape(row['weight_shape'])} \"\n        f\"key={row['key']}\"\n    )\n\n\ndef print_text_report(audit: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    body = audit[\"body\"]\n    voxtell = audit[\"voxtell\"]\n    print(\"SP-A.P0 VoxTell compatibility baseline\")\n    print()\n    print(\"Body-Tell current\")\n    print(f\"  config: {body['config_path']}\")\n    print(f\"  num_heads: {body['num_heads']}\")\n    print(\n        \"  fused projection stages: \"\n        f\"{body['fused_stage_count_actual']} \"\n        f\"(configured {body['num_maskformer_stages_config']})\"\n    )\n    for row in body[\"projection_rows\"]:\n        print(projection_line(row))\n    print()\n    print(\"VoxTell v1.1 source default\")\n    print(f\"  num_heads: {voxtell['source_default']['num_heads']}\")\n    for row in voxtell[\"source_default\"][\"projection_rows\"]:\n        print(projection_line(row))\n    print()\n    print(\"VoxTell v1.1 predictor/checkpoint profile\")\n    print(f\"  predictor num_heads: {voxtell['predictor_v1_1']['num_heads']}\")\n    if voxtell[\"checkpoint\"] and voxtell[\"checkpoint\"].get(\"available\"):\n        print(f\"  checkpoint: {voxtell['checkpoint']['checkpoint_path']}\")\n        print(f\"  checkpoint keys: {voxtell['checkpoint']['key_count']}\")\n        print(f\"  checkpoint pos_embed: {fmt_shape(voxtell['checkpoint']['pos_embed_shape'])}\")\n        print(f\"  checkpoint inferred num_heads: {voxtell['checkpoint_num_heads']}\")\n        for row in voxtell[\"checkpoint\"][\"projection_rows\"]:\n            print(projection_line(row))\n    elif voxtell[\"checkpoint\"]:\n        print(f\"  checkpoint unavailable: {voxtell['checkpoint']['error']}\")\n    else:\n        print(\"  checkpoint inspection skipped\")\n        for row in voxtell[\"predictor_v1_1\"][\"projection_rows\"]:\n            print(projection_line(row))\n    print()\n    print(\"P6 whitelist input\")\n    for item in audit[\"whitelist_input\"][\"required_exact_skip_patterns\"]:\n        print(f\"  required skip: {item['pattern']} ({item['reason']})\")\n    for item in audit[\"whitelist_input\"][\"conditional_skip_patterns\"]:\n        print(f\"  conditional skip: {item['pattern']} ({item['reason']})\")\n    for note in audit[\"whitelist_input\"][\"no_skip_notes\"]:\n        print(f\"  note: {note}\")\n    compare = audit[\"state_compare_current_body_vs_checkpoint\"]\n    if compare[\"available\"]:\n        print()\n        print(\"Current Body-Tell same-name checkpoint shape coverage\")\n        print(f\"  matching keys: {compare['matching_count']}\")\n        print(f\"  shape mismatches: {compare['mismatch_count']}\")\n        print(f\"  missing in checkpoint: {compare['missing_in_checkpoint_count']}\")\n        print(f\"  unexpected in checkpoint: {compare['unexpected_in_checkpoint_count']}\")\n        print(f\"  matched params: {compare['matched_param_count']:,} / {compare['body_param_count']:,}\")\n\n\ndef table_row(cells: list[Any], code_first: bool = False) -> str:\n    rendered = []\n    for index, cell in enumerate(cells):\n        value = html.escape(str(cell))\n        if code_first and index == 0:\n            value = f\"<code>{value}</code>\"\n        rendered.append(f\"<td>{value}</td>\")\n    return \"<tr>\" + \"\".join(rendered) + \"</tr>\"\n\n\ndef projection_table(rows: list[dict[str, Any]]) -> str:\n    body = \"\\n\".join(\n        table_row(\n            [\n                row[\"stage\"],\n                row.get(\"channels\", \"n/a\"),\n                row[\"output_dim\"],\n                fmt_shape(row[\"weight_shape\"]),\n                row[\"key\"],\n            ]\n        )\n        for row in rows\n    )\n    return (\n        \"<table><thead><tr>\"\n        \"<th>Stage</th><th>Channels</th><th>Output dim</th><th>Final linear weight</th><th>Key</th>\"\n        \"</tr></thead><tbody>\"\n        f\"{body}</tbody></table>\"\n    )\n\n\ndef render_html_report(audit: dict[str, Any]) -> str:\n    body = audit[\"body\"]\n    voxtell = audit[\"voxtell\"]\n    compare = audit[\"state_compare_current_body_vs_checkpoint\"]\n    whitelist = audit[\"whitelist_input\"]\n    checkpoint = voxtell[\"checkpoint\"]\n    checkpoint_rows = (\n        checkpoint[\"projection_rows\"]\n        if checkpoint and checkpoint.get(\"available\")\n        else voxtell[\"predictor_v1_1\"][\"projection_rows\"]\n    )\n    checkpoint_label = \"checkpoint-derived\" if checkpoint and checkpoint.get(\"available\") else \"predictor-derived\"\n\n    prefix_table = \"\"\n    if compare[\"available\"]:\n        prefix_rows = \"\\n\".join(\n            table_row(\n                [\n                    row[\"prefix\"],\n                    row[\"body_keys\"],\n                    row[\"checkpoint_keys\"],\n                    row[\"shape_compatible_same_name\"],\n                ],\n                code_first=True,\n            )\n            for row in compare[\"prefix_rows\"]\n        )\n        prefix_table = (\n            \"<table><thead><tr><th>Prefix</th><th>Body keys</th><th>Checkpoint keys</th>\"\n            \"<th>Same-name shape-compatible</th></tr></thead><tbody>\"\n            f\"{prefix_rows}</tbody></table>\"\n        )\n\n    required_skip_rows = \"\\n\".join(\n        table_row([item[\"pattern\"], item[\"reason\"]], code_first=True)\n        for item in whitelist[\"required_exact_skip_patterns\"]\n    )\n    conditional_skip_rows = \"\\n\".join(\n        table_row([item[\"pattern\"], item[\"reason\"]], code_first=True)\n        for item in whitelist[\"conditional_skip_patterns\"]\n    )\n    no_skip_notes = \"\".join(\n        f\"<li>{html.escape(note)}</li>\" for note in whitelist[\"no_skip_notes\"]\n    )\n\n    embedded_json = html.escape(json.dumps(audit, indent=2, sort_keys=True, default=str))\n    return f\"\"\"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <title>SP-A.P0 VoxTell Alignment Audit</title>\n  <style>\n    body {{ font: 15px/1.55 -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif; margin: 0; color: #17202a; background: #f6f8fa; }}\n    main {{ max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px 56px; }}\n    section {{ background: #fff; border: 1px solid #d8e0e7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px 20px; margin: 16px 0; }}\n    h1 {{ margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 28px; }}\n    h2 {{ margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 20px; }}\n    table {{ border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 14px; }}\n    th, td {{ border: 1px solid #d8e0e7; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }}\n    th {{ background: #eef3f7; }}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
